    "Afterwards, collinearity analysis was carried out.",
    "All variance inflation factors (VIFs) of the constructs were below the acceptable limit of 5 (Hair et al., 2021).",
    "Table 2 and Fig. 2 show the results.",
    "An assessment of Convergent and Discriminant validity was conducted for the measurement model.",
    "AVE, loading, and composite reliability are examined for assessing convergent validity."
